data.description: Beautiful home in Fair Oaks!  Spacious 5 bedroom 3 bath with high ceilings, open floor plan, 3-car garage as well as an additional dining/flex room/study.  Well equipped kitchen with huge island, stainless steel appliances, plenty of counter and lots of cabinet storage.  Lovely natural lighting throughout the house as well as a large backyard with a covered patio perfect for evening meals outside.  The master suite includes spacious living quarters, a luxurious bathroom in addition to a huge walk-in closet.
